   version stable 0.5 0.4 20070516 20070508
   require dmenu xmessage
  category window-manager
 attribute x11 library
    source http://code.suckless.org/dl/libs/libixp-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info home http://repo.cat-v.org/libixp/
      desc 'stand-alone client/server 9P library including ixpc client'

